title: Grateful Dead Live at Greensboro Coliseum on 1981-04-30
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, Peggy-O-> CC Rider, Alabama Getaway-> Greatest Story Ever Told, Loser-> Looks Like Rain, China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider

Set 2

Shakedown Street-> Samson & Delilah, It Must Have Been The Roses, Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> Truckin'-> Black Peter-> Around & Around-> Johnny B. Goode, E: Casey Jones
